sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Gateway API HTTPRoute<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy Sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Upstream as Upstream Application<br/>HTTP/HTTPS/h2c
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>(openshift-monitoring)
    participant OIDC as OIDC Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over Client,Upstream: Flow 1: Authenticated Request via Bearer Token
        Client->>Gateway: HTTPS/8443<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        Gateway->>Proxy: HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS 1.2+
        Proxy->>K8sAPI: POST /apis/authentication.k8s.io/v1/tokenreviews<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
        K8sAPI-->>Proxy: TokenReview Result<br/>(user identity, groups)
        Proxy->>K8sAPI: POST /apis/authorization.k8s.io/v1/subjectaccessreviews<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
        K8sAPI-->>Proxy: SubjectAccessReview Result<br/>(allowed: true/false)
        alt Authorized
            Proxy->>Upstream: Forward Request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS/h2c<br/>+ X-Forwarded-User, X-Forwarded-Groups headers
            Upstream-->>Proxy: Response
            Proxy-->>Gateway: HTTPS Response
            Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS Response
        else Denied
            Proxy-->>Gateway: 403 Forbidden
            Gateway-->>Client: 403 Forbidden
        end
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over Prometheus,Upstream: Flow 2: Prometheus Metrics Scraping (Hardcoded Allow)
        Prometheus->>Proxy: GET /metrics<br/>HTTPS/8443<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (prometheus-k8s SA)
        Note over Proxy: Hardcoded Authorizer:<br/>Auto-allows system:serviceaccount:<br/>openshift-monitoring:prometheus-k8s<br/>(no API call needed)
        Proxy->>Upstream: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP (localhost)
        Upstream-->>Proxy: Metrics Response<br/>(Prometheus format)
        Proxy-->>Prometheus: Metrics Response<br/>HTTPS
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Client,Upstream: Flow 3: OIDC JWT Authentication
        Client->>Gateway: HTTPS/8443<br/>Auth: Bearer JWT (OIDC)
        Gateway->>Proxy: HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS 1.2+
        Proxy->>OIDC: GET /.well-known/openid-configuration<br/>HTTPS/443
        OIDC-->>Proxy: OIDC Discovery Document
        Proxy->>OIDC: GET /jwks<br/>HTTPS/443
        OIDC-->>Proxy: JWKS (signing keys)
        Note over Proxy: Validate JWT signature,<br/>map claims to user/groups
        Proxy->>K8sAPI: POST SubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
        K8sAPI-->>Proxy: SAR Result (allowed)
        Proxy->>Upstream: Forward Request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS<br/>+ user/group headers
        Upstream-->>Proxy: Response
        Proxy-->>Gateway: HTTPS Response
        Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS Response
    end
